<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聖誕節要煩惱的事情好多啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是交換禮物時，<delay20 />什麼樣的禮物<delay20 />
才能讓收到的人高興<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了……<delay20 />反正不管是多麼微薄的禮物，<delay20 />
只要用包裝紙包裝一下，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />收到的人都會很開心吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在平安夜這一天<delay20 />
所發生的任何事情，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都會變得格外特別<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要一想到我送出的聖誕禮物<delay20 />
有可能會點綴某個人的人生片段……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來我得滿懷愛意地送出禮物才行啊。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有看過裝飾在廣場那邊的樹嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到被裝飾得色彩繽紛的杉樹，<delay20 />
就有種「聖誕節到了！」的感覺呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有了這麼醒目的地標，<delay20 />
以後約會就不怕沒有會合地點了。<10_4 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我<delay20 />暫時沒那種安排就是了<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
</msbt>